The Wonderful World of Mickey Mouse: Steamboat Silly

description.brief: Mickey and gang must stop hundreds of film reel versions of Mickey from wreaking havoc across town.
description.medium: Mickey and gang must stop hundreds of old film reel versions of Mickey from wreaking havoc all over town.
description.full: Mickey takes a stroll down memory lane by watching old home movies, but when he accidentally unleashes hundreds of "Steamboat Willie" Mickeys from the film reel, he and the gang must stop them from wreaking havoc on the town with their old cartoon antics.

visuals.title: The Wonderful World of Mickey Mouse

description.brief: It's nothing but fun for Mickey and friends as they embark on their greatest adventures yet.
description.medium: It's nothing but fun and excitement for Mickey Mouse and his best friends as they embark on their greatest adventures yet, navigating the pitfalls and curveballs of a wild and crazy world where the magic of Disney makes the impossible possible.
description.full: It's nothing but fun and excitement for Mickey Mouse and his best friends as they embark on their greatest adventures yet, navigating the pitfalls and curveballs of a wild and crazy world where the magic of Disney makes the impossible possible.

description.brief: All-new series of cartoon shorts, Mickey Mouse finds himself in silly situations around the world!
description.medium: In this all-new series of cartoon shorts, Mickey Mouse finds himself in silly situations around the world! Mickey experiences new adventures with his friends! After Minnies caf runs out of croissants, Mickey must race to her rescue battling street traffic and other Parisian obstacles along the way. On the hottest day of the year, Mickey, Donald and Goofy must find creative ways to keep cool!
description.full: With the slapstick feel of classic Mickey Mouse, the series of cartoon shorts presents Mickey in a broad range of humorous situations that showcase his pluck and rascality, along with his long-beloved charm and good heartedness. Each cartoon short finds Mickey in a different contemporary setting including Santa Monica, New York, Paris, Beijing, Tokyo, Venice and the Alps, facing a silly situation, a quick complication and an escalation of physical and visual gags. The stories also feature genuine heartfelt and heroic moments as Mickey explores and experiences life with his comical partners: Minnie Mouse, Donald Duck, Daisy Duck, Goofy, and Pluto.

description.brief: Mickey and friends enjoy skating on a frozen river.
description.medium: Mickey and friends have various levels of enjoyment skating on a frozen river. As Mickey and Minnie glide romantically, Donald plays tricks on Pluto and ends up in trouble himself with a kite, from which Mickey must save him.
description.full: Mickey and friends have various levels of enjoyment skating on a frozen river. As Mickey and Minnie glide romantically, Donald plays tricks on Pluto and ends up in trouble himself with a kite, from which Mickey must save him.

description.brief: Donald and his nephews play Hockey.
description.medium: Donald attempts to show off his hockey abilities to his nephews, but their skill finally gets the best of him.
description.full: Donald, "The Hockey Champion of Duck Swamp" challenges his nephews to a hockey game. But his constant showing off eventually leads to his downfall.
